---
title: Chermoula Pork & Roast Veggie Couscous with Mint & Yoghurt
description: Spiced, succulent, and seriously satisfying—this dish is a flavour-packed adventure! Juicy, chermoula-marinated pork meets roasted root veggies and fluffy couscous for the perfect balance of smokey, sweet, and savoury. A dollop of cooling yoghurt ties it all together for a fresh and vibrant finish. One bite, and you’ll be hooked!
